    "However, further testing across a broader spectrum of software projects-including real-time systems, AI-driven applications, and games-is essential to fully understand the applicability and limitations of LLMs in these varied contexts.",
    "Additionally, exploring different requirements specifications and design methodologies is crucial to assess the adaptability and effectiveness of LLMs in diverse software engineering paradigms.",
    "While a tailored version of ChatGPT has been developed and made publicly available, utilizing the default user interface of ChatGPT for software development presents practical challenges.",
    "Specifically, software engineers may find it cumbersome to navigate through previously generated designs or code snippets due to the need to scroll extensively.",
    "To address this issue, we envisage the creation of a user-friendly web application in future work."
